Travel Ban Protesters Asked If They'd Let Refugees Live In Their Homes, Watch How They Respond… Published February 9, 2017 Facebook 0 Twitter 0 livefyre 0 Email Print 
By Nickarama | Young Conservatives 
Video prankster Joey Salads wanted to find out what would happen if he approached leftists protesting President Donald Trump’s travel ban and asked them to take in some refugees.
